elias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/02\/love-ansar-companions-faith\/","url_meta":{"origin":32898,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Ansar: Love for companions is part of faith","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 2, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Bara' reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNone loves the Ansar but a believer, and none hates them but a hypocrite. Whoever loves them, Allah will love him. Whoever hates them, Allah will hate him.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3783, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 75 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3185,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/05\/13\/jihad-women-defense-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":32898,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Jihad: Women participate in defense of Islam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 13, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would go into battle with Umm Sulaym and a group of women with her from the Ansar; they would give water and tend to the wounded. Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1575 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8733,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/23\/entertainment-wedding-ansar\/","url_meta":{"origin":32898,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Entertainment: The Prophet entertains Ansar for a wedding","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 23, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: She prepared a lady for marriage to a man among the Ansar. The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Aisha, do you have any entertainment? Verily, the Ansar are fond of entertainment.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 4868 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Bukhari Badr al-Din al-'Ayni said, \"The\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8735,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/24\/prophet-singers-weddings\/","url_meta":{"origin":32898,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Songs: The Prophet allows singers at weddings","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 24, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: Aisha gave away one of her relatives in marriage to a man among the Ansar. The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, came and he said, \u201cDid you send them a girl?\u201d They said yes. The Prophet said, \u201cDid you send someone to sing\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6826,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/21\/ansar-prefer-others-themselves\/","url_meta":{"origin":32898,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Altruism: Believers prefer others over their own selves","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 21, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: A man from the Ansar was hosting a guest and he had nothing with him but just enough food for himself and his children. The man said to his wife, \u201cPut the children to sleep, put out the lamp, and serve our guest with what we have.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24733,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/04\/24\/no-true-life-but-akhirah\/","url_meta":{"origin":32898,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Akhirah: No true life but the Hereafter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 24, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Allah, there is no life worth living but the life of the Hereafter, so be generous to the Ansar and the Muhajirun.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3796, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1805 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/32898","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\